Sentencas: BaZr0.5Y0.5O3(BZY) electrolyte exhibited enormous potential for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) due to its proton dominant mobile carriers rather than oxygen ions during the electrochemical process.
Titulo: Compositing protonic conductor BaZr0.5Y0.5O3 (BZY) with triple conductor BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ (BCFZY) as electrolyte for advanced solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In order to enhance the ionic conductivity, triple conductor BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-delta (BCFZY) was composited with proton conductor BZY to form semiconductor-ionic conductor composite (SIM), which was applied as electrolyte to fabricate symmetrical fuel cell.
Titulo: Compositing protonic conductor BaZr0.5Y0.5O3 (BZY) with triple conductor BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ (BCFZY) as electrolyte for advanced solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The microstructural and electrochemical properties for BZY, BCFZY and BZY-BCFZY composites were studied.
Titulo: Compositing protonic conductor BaZr0.5Y0.5O3 (BZY) with triple conductor BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ (BCFZY) as electrolyte for advanced solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: After optimizing the weight ratio of composite content, the ionic conductivity and electronic conductivity reached an equilibrium state to obtain the maximum cell performance, namely the highest output of 902.5 mW cm(-2) and an open circuit voltage (OCV) of 1.043 V at 550 degrees C.
Titulo: Compositing protonic conductor BaZr0.5Y0.5O3 (BZY) with triple conductor BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ (BCFZY) as electrolyte for advanced solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The BZY-BCFZY cell also presented decent power output at low temperature, a power density of 265.625 mW cm(-2) was received even at 500 degrees C, demonstrating that the BZY-BCFZY composite was a potential electrolyte for low temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: Compositing protonic conductor BaZr0.5Y0.5O3 (BZY) with triple conductor BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ (BCFZY) as electrolyte for advanced solid oxide fuel cell
